Class StringRequestBody

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scvngr.levelup.core.net.StringRequestBody
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable, RequestBody
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JSONArrayRequestBody, JsonElementRequestBody, JSONObjectRequestBody

    @Immutable
@ThreadSafe
@LevelUpApi(contract=DRAFT)
public abstract class StringRequestBody
extends Object
implements RequestBody

    A simple RequestBody that stores the body as a String.

    As this implements the Parcelable interface, subclasses must fully implement the Parcelable interface. This includes having both constructors that this class defines, as well as the public static final Parcelable.Creator CREATOR.
